The application is designed to make the planting process easier to manage. 

On the home screen menu, you have the option to select the consumable plant you have planted.Then, the plant will appear in the journal.

The app integrates technology to make the entire plant-growing process more convenient. 

Freddy provides information to clarify any questions the user may have on this topic. 

He is capable of analyzing photos to offer details about the plant and the care it requires.

For the plants in the agenda, the app will record the planting date, the current growth stage, 

the estimated harvest date, and watering reminders, which Freddy manages based on the specific needs of each plant species.

Additionally, the application includes a community chat feature.
